formattedAddress: #B1-10, The Star Vista (1 Vista Exchange Green)

tip.text: Go look for custom shop and do wear Korean custom must look for those as grand as possible and you will not regret
I go there only for the Vietnamese food.  I like their spring roll, pork chop rice and lots more
The white Mee hon is really good, at other places you mind have kind of oily taste but not here.   The only things I want them to improve is don't make the Mee hon too soft.
The curry Horfan is really great but be aware of their price cuz the are using premium ingredients
Favourite always the Claypot yong tofu!  Of course all their food are really great make you feel how the 70's Chinatown street food supposed to be
The fries are fantastic and of course the fry chicken itself is much better than lots of Korean fry chicken in JB
Local dishes are really great!  I have laksa, satay and rojak all these are make in premium grade and good old fashion ways.
果然雲吞麵加上生熟蛋是好吃！

tip.text: Love their fry chicken much nice than those so call Korean fry chicken restaurants in JB
這裡的招牌粉一流，記得叫豆腐與魚片，再醮他們的辣椒醬，爽辣！
這𥚃的服務一流，出菜也快，最重要是雞肉是給足，在其他地方是薄紙幾片。而且他們的飯不會太爑。
今天發現除了冰鎮奶茶好喝外，原鴛鴦的喝法可以提升，茶啡共舞可以一試！
